[[div class="material-box"]]
[[div class="title-style"]]
Investigative Report:
[[/div]]

Research personnel were administered Class-W Mnestic[[footnote]]**Mnestic:** An agent used to temporarily enhance a user's immediate memory retention.[[/footnote]] drugs with the intent to examine SCP-4031. Personnel discovered a hereto unaccounted for male subject on the floor, deceased. The subject possessed lacerations, emaciation, a broken left clavicle, and blood loss in the oral cavity.

Most notably, the subject possessed [[[a-kind-of-redemption|significant cranial damage.]]]
